events.description:
Alert Level: Information
Reported (UTC): 2019-01-28T04:41:31
Current Status: Patrolled
Details: There is a vegetation fire at this location. Smoke may affect residents and motorists in the area. Residents should close their doors and windows and keep medication close by if suffering from a respiratory condition. Motorists should use caution and drive to conditions. If you believe your property is under threat, you should call Triple Zero (000) immediately.
